Roy Roberts https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roy_Roberts 0 Roy Roberts (born Roy Barnes Jones, March 19, 1906 – May 28, 1975) was an American character actor. Over his more than 40-year career, he appeared in more than nine hundred productions on stage and screen.
